OL,3,CThree men charged after intruder shot
OL,4,Cdead in burglaries
OL,6,FThree men have been charged in
OL,7,Fconnection with burglaries where an
OL,8,Fintruder was shot dead by the
OL,9,Fhomeowner.
OL,11,FMarcus Smith, 19, from Chapel-en-le-
OL,12,FFrith died after police were called to
OL,13,Fthe remote property on Eccles Road in
OL,14,FWhaley Bridge, Derbyshire, on 1 May
OL,15,F2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
