PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784715503
OL,3,CThree men charged after intruder shot
OL,4,Cdead in burglaries
OL,6,FThe homeowner - a man in his 50s - was
OL,7,Finitially arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fmurder but the Crown Prosecution
OL,9,FService (CPS) has confirmed he would
OL,10,Fnot face criminal charges in relation
OL,11,Fto the death of Mr Smith and serious
OL,12,Finjuries to another person on his
OL,13,Fproperty.
OL,15,FIt said the homeowner discharged a
OL,16,Flegally held firearm when confronted
OL,17,Fwith burglars in his home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
