PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784715503
OL,3,CThree men charged after intruder shot
OL,4,Cdead in burglaries
OL,6,FIt confirmed three men would face
OL,7,Fproceedings for burglary in relation
OL,8,Fto the incident and a burglary at the
OL,9,Fsame property the night before.
OL,11,FJack Cooper, 22, of Sparrowpit, and
OL,12,FReece Nadin, 20, of Horderns Road,
OL,13,FChapel-en-le-Frith, have been charged
OL,14,Fwith burglary.
OL,16,FCooper has also been charged with a
OL,17,Fburglary at the same property between
OL,18,F29 and 30 April 2024, alongside
OL,19,FFrederick Andric, 32, of Buxton Road
OL,20,Fin Chapel-en-le-Frith.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
