PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784715503
OL,3,CThree men charged after intruder shot
OL,4,Cdead in burglaries
OL,6,FAll three have been released on bail
OL,7,Fto appear at Southern Derbyshire
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court on 17 August.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
